    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134300/extras/f91fc376434935d74358b0b4e7a6348e.avif?t=1675259173\" width=620 height=129 /></span><br><br>ParkTo is a simple puzzle game that stops the car at its destination.<br><br>You don't drive a car yourself. The car just moves forward'. <br>Use the given triggers to move the car to its destination: LEFT, RIGHT, STOP, BACKWARD, etc. <br>Triggers can be placed on the path of the car or used on the car itself. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134300/extras/bffa4d7599ccde2bb20bd32bdd98cbfe.poster.avif?t=1675259173\" width=620 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134300/extras/bffa4d7599ccde2bb20bd32bdd98cbfe.webm?t=1675259173\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134300/extras/bffa4d7599ccde2bb20bd32bdd98cbfe.mp4?t=1675259173\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FEATURES</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 48 handcrafted levels. </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Various trigger interactions reflecting car movements. </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Comfortable colors and minimal graphics. </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> You can play without a driving license! </li></ul>",
